                             <div class="caption slide-copy">
                              <h2>
                               <a href="https://youthprotection.harvard.edu/guidelines">
                                Keeping Kids Safe is Everyone's Job
                               </a>
                              </h2>
                              <p>
                               <a href="https://youthprotection.harvard.edu/guidelines">
                                It's on all of us - faculty, staff, &amp; the community - to promote a safe environment for youth in our Programs &amp; on our campuses
