                <div class="boxes-box-content">
                 <p>
                  Harvard University is committed to providing a safe environment for everyone on its campuses and in its programs, including the thousands of minors who participate in programs and activities both on and off campus.
                 </p>
                 <p>
                  <em>
                   <a href="https://youthprotection.harvard.edu/minors/guidelines">
                    Members of the Harvard community who interact with minors
                   </a>
                  </em>
                  in any official capacity are expected to foster and maintain an appropriate and secure environment for minors, and
                  <em>
                   <a href="https://youthprotection.harvard.edu/minors/reporting">
                    report suspected abuse or neglect of minors
                   </a>
                  </em>
                  and other inappropriate activity involving minors.
                 </p>
                </div>
               </div>
              </div>
             </div>
            </div>
